<br>
Slow 'em, root 'em and beat them down.  Getting singles isn't hard, but the pathing is horrible so care is needed when pulling.  Keep them rooted so they don't kill the slower and it isn't too bad.<br>
<br>
You could realistically do them with:<br>
<br>
Warrior/Pally/SK<br>
Chanter/Shaman<br>
Cleric<br>
Monk/rogue/ranger/mage/wizard/druid/bard/necro/shaman<br>
<br>
Assuming all are 58+, 60 prefered for the tank so that taunt works.<br>
<br>
